<s> I recently received a document whose signature failed to verify, the error being that the Signature element could not be found because the name space had changed.  </s>
<s> The document used: while the verifier expected In the latest spec it's  </s>
<s> How does this work in the real world?  </s>
<s> Assuming that the spec will not be frozen forever, does the name space keep changing?  </s>
<s> Doesn't this affect interoperability?  </s>
<s> Does the specification change, but the name space stays the same?  </s>
<s> Would the software have to keep an ever growing  </s>
<s> list of name spaces it supports, and run down the list every time it's looking for an element in the DOM tree?  </s>
